text: Ivanovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Shabagishsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 107 as of 2010. There are 6 streets.Карта Куюргазинского района Башкортостана == Geography == It is located 16 km from Yermolayevo, 4 km from Shabagish. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Ivanovka, Kuyurgazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
